=============================================================================
EDUCATIONAL USE NOTE
=============================================================================

This repository contains educational Python course materials specifically
designed for blind and visually impaired learners. You are encouraged to:

- Use these materials for personal learning
- Share them with students, educators, and accessibility advocates
- Adapt them for other accessible educational contexts
- Translate them to support learners in different languages

When sharing or adapting, please credit the original creator:
  Mahmoud Shaabo - suleimanAlQusaimi Python Course
  https://github.com/mahmoudshaabo1984/suleimanAlQusaimiPythonCourse

